{"generated": "2026-07-16 20:11", "curation": {"market": "개인 투자자 여러분께,\n\n지난 24시간 동안 국내 증시는 반도체 업황 우려와 금리 인상이라는 이중 악재 속에서 큰 폭의 하락세를 보였습니다. 주요 테마별로 자세히 살펴보겠습니다.\n\n<b>반도체 업황 우려 및 주가 급락</b>\n국내 증시의 핵심인 반도체 업황에 대한 우려가 재확산되면서 관련주가 큰 폭으로 하락했습니다. 삼성전자 8.8%, SK하이닉스 11.5% 급락을 포함해 반도체 종목들이 전반적으로 부진했으며, 이는 코스피가 하루 만에 6%대 급락하며 7,000선과 6,800선마저 내주는 주요 원인이 되었습니다. AI 투자 둔화 우려와 산업장관의 \"반도체 외 어렵다\"는 발언도 이러한 심리를 부추겼습니다. [<a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMia0FVX3lxTE9rbHNBS0Y1QnBzSk81SXBqMk9NQmZ4YjhzSzFkV3V0eGIxTnFEbF9BNS1WZjJmWkh5MW9MQl9rcFY2S0F2VVM3d3hMLWJUNEFOVEFvSmlCWlNMalNxS0xGR0hXblFJY19FbWFV?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#3</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiT0FVX3lxTE50QjNwbXlkZlY2N3JxdXJYQUgwQmlvVWZxNUp1UC1RMzBMQzZ2eGNlVUNQanFUSDBzNG1wd3VKTXROamFTdFA3UlJvUXZtWFE?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#6</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMidkFVX3lxTE8zUDRGcmp0ZEgwMjg4bEpvUTV6dVBlckM3cFIxeFluUWx2cGJPc2lyaHhrYzVzVWNlOElldVlmTGdfT0RpbnBLazM0SENjWmxDWmQ2b3hoM2k3cFdwSzNYQVg5VmxqVDgxREZCck9jLXFvNTl4ekE?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#9</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMibEFVX3lxTE45VjJZbFdEeUFwUFo3cmFvOGNwSndBN04yRm5ieFBHdWYtNXg5RTh2VzZ6ZWJXX0otU1d6TmIxMkhNSmVsOVYxQVZQMmNUYXk2WVJiN2kzNkNHV2dCOVE4bGwyTGc0NWlRXzJiVQ?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#10</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMibkFVX3lxTFBIdmVCT0ljM3p0WXd5WXpJa2tXdlZsdTJoSjRVdlZRZHJ2dVhKVmJQclczZUZieEhZU1R0M2gtSWMtTHE2SG1oN1pwdnJQMzg0Q1pDWXY5TUFxWE5fMGFPM2NMdWRzREltWWFtTEFB?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#11</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMicEFVX3lxTFBDVDRCTy1WR1RSNGdvTVVsWlpUQ0NGUGt6TWlyQ25OQzVxREo1bENfSHBDQUg1ZkZJS0poRnU3SDdFWmF4M1YtQWRoVG9CUGpObHMyNE9YclFfYW8walJ5RlhvRDNVR3NOUHAxeDZfYmE?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#12</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiYkFVX3lxTFBOWEROMk9VQnBDVGdtOEFSQmN3ZjlOY0hETWF2X3E2RmFQcThseUxlTTdnVWN1SzJBM